{"tid":498500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佛教協會高僧：中共十九大報告是當代佛經　共產黨是菩薩","createTime":"2017-12-14T00:40:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T03:45:13.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"8649adc29977211bcb435c49918d01a8c650b33e","tid":498500,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T00:40:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佛教協會高僧：中共十九大報告是當代佛經　共產黨是菩薩</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171213/s00004/165e302bb28b5e7b6fcb2336248387fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171213%2Fs00004%2F165e302bb28b5e7b6fcb2336248387fa.jpg&h=95bffe77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共十九大閉幕後，內地不少地方政府掀起了研習十九大報告的風潮，而在周一（11日）舉行的「海南省佛教協會學習十九大精神培訓班」上，負責主持的僧人，現任中國佛教協會副會長印順大和尚在會上表示，「共產黨就是現世的佛菩薩」，又指「十九大報告就是當代的佛經，我已經手抄了三遍，而且還要準備再抄十遍」。<br />\n<br />\n印順表示：「佛教徒首先要做一個愛國愛黨的守法公民，然後才談得上佛教信仰。離開了現實談佛國，離開當下談未來，離開了民眾談修行，一切宗教都失去了存在的意義。」<br />\n<br />\n他又倡議佛教徒應該可以像他一樣，「以恭敬心手抄十九大報告，抄一遍有一遍的體悟和收穫」，並稱他所屬的佛教協會及會員，應該「樹立『中華佛教愛國形象』，講好『中華佛教愛國故事』，人人都成為十九大精神的優秀宣講員」。<br />\n<br />\n（鳳凰網/海南南海佛學院）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171213/s00004/1513154774237\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171213%2Fs00004%2F1513154774237&d=yokb69uU2TaPlFT3jV6eC0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=9ee144a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171213%2Fs00004%2F1513154774237&h=954ec934\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171213/s00004/1513154774237</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95504f6897744aa65f36b21ffa7567fd2092bd0c","tid":498500,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T00:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea9754e5126ac4c7524cea8d45398fa94145cae","tid":498500,"uid":131064,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T00:53:46.000Z","msg":"耳尖尖，古惑<br />\n鼻尖尖，攻心計<br />\n<br />\n非姦即盜"},{"pid":"5c5f747e6990b83012f6b1e1a14292a41d2115ea","tid":498500,"uid":28195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T00:54:14.000Z","msg":"去佛寺參佛俾香油真係好on9<br />\n<br />\n好多人貪心or惡貫滿盈先會俾錢拜佛"},{"pid":"fdc50960533b56efaccd000ab8e77d68933b7824","tid":498500,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T00:54:23.000Z","msg":"睇個樣都係酒肉穿腸過 佛祖心中留"},{"pid":"7d433ee73906288cf8c580a0fe190cc7ab77e559","tid":498500,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T00:54:35.000Z","msg":"無恥到，賊禿"},{"pid":"7510e6cce4d6a5bb586b5ac80fa19aae2c1a0b4c","tid":498500,"uid":30782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T01:01:04.000Z","msg":"屌，大陸d 和尚咪又係假既，唔咁講又點呃飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da774853f57e3e21b7d8b84348fca5829ea4a6d","tid":498500,"uid":47674,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T01:03:03.000Z","msg":"不如早午晚課梵音唱誦十九大報告<br />\n「尾油尾油尾油尾油尾油......通過」"},{"pid":"b8bd4994ff63fd1cf950c4d5c35f84c81038b8b0","tid":498500,"uid":54516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T01:06:02.000Z","msg":"將濕鳩大報告錄入電子唸佛機，播足3.5小時。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af313d1a0f4681958f2b3b8a0425ffa5429aee15","tid":498500,"uid":28195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T01:06:45.000Z","msg":"香港攪個習廟，拜習菩薩，有無得諗？"},{"pid":"912ccdcd19fcee37e3953339f731baaa7f56b8f6","tid":498500,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T01:09:10.000